<p> </p>";i:2;s:0:"";i:3;s:28:"&w=100%&h=300px&edt=TinyMCE4";i:4;s:8:"richtext";}s:25:"issueArticleFootnotesText";a:5:{i:0;s:25:"issueArticleFootnotesText";i:1;s:15645:"<p><a href="#sdfootnote1anc" name="sdfootnote1sym">1</a> Joseph Warton, <em>The World</em> no. 26 (June 28, 1753), 155. Emphasis in the original.</p>
